00:04:53,010 --> 00:04:55,140
Perfect. Let me see the values.

88
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:58,470
Yep, we have the correct value this time

89
00:04:58,470 --> 00:04:59,973
and that looks good.

90
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:03,330
So our migration is looking good.

91
00:05:03,330 --> 00:05:05,320
Let me update the database

92
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:13,650
And perfect. That is done.

